# Expo Public Environment Variables
# Instructions: Copy this file to .env (it's already done in your project)

# Backend API URL - AUTO-DETECTION ENABLED BY DEFAULT
# =====================================================
# The app automatically detects your computer's IP address from Expo.
# This allows team members to work on any network without manual configuration.
#
# LEAVE THIS COMMENTED OUT for automatic detection:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://YOUR_IP:3001
#
# Only uncomment and set manually if:
# 1. You're using an Android emulator: http://10.0.2.2:3001
# 2. Auto-detection fails on your setup
# 3. You need to connect to a specific server
#
# For physical devices and iOS simulators: Let it auto-detect!
